Package: HMSC
Type: Package
Title: Hierarchical Modelling of Species Community
Version: 2.1-2
Date: 2018-05-07
Author: F. Guillaume Blanchet, with contributions from Gleb Tikhonov and Anna Norberg
Maintainer: F. Guillaume Blanchet <guillaume.blanchet@usherbrooke.ca>
Description: Implement a general framework to analyze species community data
    using Bayesian hierarchical models. All estimations are carried out using Markov chain Monte Carlo.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Suggests: circlize, beanplot, corrplot
Depends:
    R (>= 2.10),
    MASS,
    coda,
    Rcpp (>= 0.12.3),
    RcppArmadillo
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
SystemRequirements: C++11
